572
00:40:15,110 --> 00:40:16,320
For me,

573
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:21,110
he killed the man he always took
to be his father.

574
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:24,800
Wang Liang,

575
00:40:26,550 --> 00:40:27,550
a man

576
00:40:27,550 --> 00:40:29,360
I've never looked up to

577
00:40:30,590 --> 00:40:31,800
has done everything for me,

578
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:34,710
no matter that he should
or should not have done.

579
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:38,920
He's silly.

580
00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:41,320
Who can prove you're telling the truth?

581
00:40:43,630 --> 00:40:45,550
You put the blame of murder
on Wang Liang

582
00:40:45,550 --> 00:40:46,880
