583
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:49,110
Why should I clear my name?

584
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:55,920
Whether it's killing Liu Sancheng
or Liu Dazhi,

585
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,320
it's all my order.

586
00:40:57,960 --> 00:40:58,880
If I didn't order it,

587
00:40:58,880 --> 00:41:00,400
Wang Liang wouldn't have done it.

588
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,230
Can my name still be cleared?

589
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:05,760
Wang Liang killed
your adoptive father for you,

590
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:09,400
the fire in your heart
should be extinguished.

591
00:41:10,070 --> 00:41:11,710
Why did you still want
to kill your brother?

592
00:41:12,510 --> 00:41:13,920
When your adoptive mother died,

593
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,710
you were eight and he was six.

594
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:17,800
You also said

595
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:20,150
your brother grew up on your back.

596
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,320
How could you bring yourself to do that?

597
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:23,510
Yes.

598
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:27,400
After Liu Sancheng died,

599
00:41:27,960 --> 00:41:30,110
the fire in my heart was extinguished.

600
00:41:30,510 --> 00:41:31,920
And I didn't dislike Wang Liang

601
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:34,710
as much as before.

602
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:37,150
I sometimes thought

603
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:39,710
