606
00:41:48,150 --> 00:41:50,320
and I wouldn't kill Liu Dazhi.

607
00:41:51,150 --> 00:41:52,030
Anyway,

608
00:41:54,110 --> 00:41:57,030
Liu Dazhi forced me to do it.

609
00:41:58,590 --> 00:41:59,960
He came out of the police station

610
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:02,510
and said you'd let him go

611
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:05,630
and that he wanted to leave immediately.

612
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,960
I went to the hotel to see him.

613
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:13,000
I just thought
that since things have come

614
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:14,320
to this point,

615
00:42:14,670 --> 00:42:15,710
there's something

616
