626
00:42:54,400 --> 00:42:55,190
Who?

627
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:00,030
Wang Liang.

628
00:43:00,510 --> 00:43:01,320
Wang Liang!

629
00:43:03,510 --> 00:43:04,760
Do you suspect Wang Liang?

630
00:43:06,670 --> 00:43:08,230
Who else could it be but Wang Liang?

631
00:43:08,440 --> 00:43:10,190
He's the only one who knows
what happened back then.

632
00:43:10,190 --> 00:43:11,360
