646
00:43:58,710 --> 00:44:00,190
Aren't your hands dirty enough?

647
00:44:13,360 --> 00:44:15,400
Yingying, you work in a hospital.

648
00:44:15,710 --> 00:44:18,280
You have a lot of ways
of killing people without bloodshed.

649
00:44:20,510 --> 00:44:21,710
Think of something.

650
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:29,400
It was a hindrance when Dad was around,

651
00:44:30,590 --> 00:44:31,440
but now he's dead.

652
00:44:33,840 --> 00:44:35,510
If Wang Liang is dead too,

653
00:44:36,030 --> 00:44:37,550
we'll be safe.

654
00:44:38,230 --> 00:44:40,190
You don't like Wang Liang either.

655
00:44:41,280 --> 00:44:42,360
If he's dead,

656
00:44:43,800 --> 00:44:45,110
you can find someone you like

657
00:44:46,070 --> 00:44:47,360
and have an adorable child.

658
00:44:52,030 --> 00:44:53,360
