722
00:48:26,510 --> 00:48:27,440
Liu Dazhi

723
00:48:30,320 --> 00:48:31,440
was very paranoid.

724
00:48:34,550 --> 00:48:35,760
He's hard to get close to.

725
00:48:36,320 --> 00:48:37,190
So

726
00:48:37,190 --> 00:48:39,670
I planned to let him get out himself
and get killed.

727
00:48:40,230 --> 00:48:41,510
Ding Baoyuan

728
00:48:42,400 --> 00:48:43,400
would stop him and kill him.

729
00:48:43,880 --> 00:48:46,840
Wang Liang ambushed
and killed Ding Baoyuan

730
